FBIS4-60426 "drnes101dd_94010" FBIS-NES-94-101 Daily Report 25 May 1994 Palestinian Affairs 'Arafat Said Divorcing Wife Over Financial Affairs 'Arafat Said Divorcing Wife Over Financial Affairs LD2505083394 Rome RAI Uno Television Network in Italian 0730 GMT 25 May 94 LD2505083394 Rome RAI Uno Television Network Italian BFN [Text] PLO leader Yasir 'Arafat has allegedly divorced his wife Suha al-Tawil because she is involved -- with her uncle and other relatives -- in not very clear financial affairs, non-official Palestinian sources have revealed.
